{"tid":2175533,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯: 司法系統「荷爾蒙失調」 有被告被輕輕放過 200萬人拉得9,000點會有濫捕","createTime":"2020-08-26T13:52:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-26T17:56:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2373f14e1b23aa2fed67f1e40c8ab90fcdad47d3","tid":2175533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/LRYEPVJKO5H4PNPJFKDRUG6F24/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FLRYEPVJKO5H4PNPJFKDRUG6F24%2F&d=hjP0Q4X6c9sJGZoCRXhathyAur%2Bbp9MVyOkMM5%2FMxDY%3D&h=6ee4c401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200826%2FLRYEPVJKO5H4PNPJFKDRUG6F24%2F&h=1a676c68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200826/LRYEPVJKO5H4PNPJFKDRUG6F24/</a><br />\n<br />\n何君堯突然評論法院判案，指司法系統「荷爾蒙失調」，量刑參差，質疑有被告被輕輕放過，他更提早施壓，稱新任首席大法官張舉能尚未就職，但對對方寄予厚望，希望對方就社會一些事態相關案件提出量刑指引，加重刑罰，「一旦定咁嘅罪行，起步點、量刑幾多、點罰法，要有統一思想、標準，<strong><span class=\"red\">唔係鍾意就感化、再唔係社會服務令」。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n至於他本人過去不斷被質疑在7.21事件都有嫌疑，他拒絕評論，稱「清者自清」，也一直有交代情況，並稱自己有協助警方調查，包括錄口供、寫文章等。他又認為警方並無濫捕，因「200萬人拉得9,000點會有濫捕？」"},{"pid":"d24a6782e652fb43cfc6d6e8e8dcec9c91d57ac5","tid":2175533,"uid":14211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-26T13:52:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07fea78b4dcd1d61b19c0860e92c8e8f8c62ccf8","tid":2175533,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0